      <pubDate>Mon, 18 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://dengemann.github.io/publication/sabbagh_generative_2019/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;For a high-level presentation of the main findings check-out our &lt;a href=&#34;http://dengemann.github.io/slides/P1609-OHBM2020-Sabbagh-Engemann.pdf&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt; OHBM 2020 Poster.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Or visit this Twitter thread:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote class=&#34;twitter-tweet&#34;&gt;&lt;p lang=&#34;en&#34; dir=&#34;ltr&#34;&gt;Excited to share our paper &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/NeuroImage_EiC?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@NeuroImage_EiC&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/DavSabbagh?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@DavSabbagh&lt;/a&gt; with &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/PierreAblin?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@PierreAblin&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/GaelVaroquaux?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@GaelVaroquaux&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/agramfort?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@agramfort&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://t.co/ke0wO8aqwk&#34;&gt;https://t.co/ke0wO8aqwk&lt;/a&gt; Nonlinear subject-level regression on M/EEG using linear models without source localization: theory + empirical benchmarks  Thread👇 &lt;a href=&#34;https://t.co/0vevsO3UmG&#34;&gt;pic.twitter.com/0vevsO3UmG&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;mdash; Denis A. Engemann (@dngman) &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/dngman/status/1262276285591629829?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;May 18, 2020&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
